   Program Summary: Program Direction

   Vision

   Manure and other byproducts as resources rather than wastes.

   Mission

   Develop cost-effective management practices, technologies and decision
   aids that will allow producers to capture the value of manure and other
   byproducts without degrading environmental quality or posing a threat
   to human and animal health.

   The research components of this program are:
     * Nutrient Management
     * Atmospheric Emissions
     * Pathogens


